{"tid":1609493,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"低階魔法：臭臭魔法","createTime":"2019-10-01T14:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T13:06:34.000Z","uid":263199,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"49ef93422bf4bc458eac15ca38cbb3e6ef8378ff","tid":1609493,"uid":263199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"是咁的，點解話低階呢？因為呢個魔法係冇乜攻擊力可言的，只係有強烈嘅臭味，臭過屙爛屎<br />\n<br />\n效果： 臭到仆街，1秒都已經想嘔<br />\n<br />\n缺點： 攻擊力低<br />\n                 要時間準備<br />\n<br />\n優點：元素簡單容易獲得<br />\n                效果持續<br />\n                令敵方感到想嘔<br />\n（即使肉體冇受傷，裝備冇受損，都會有debuff效果）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元素：<br />\n水樽<br />\n益力多，奶類製品，檸檬茶，或其它易發酵液體<br />\n紙巾<br />\n<br />\n制作方法：<br />\n簡單d講，塞d紙巾落去個樽到，然後倒哂d易變壞嘅野飲落去，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">然後係最重要嘅步驟</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打開個蓋，係陽光下暴曬</strong></span></span></span><br />\n時間方面，應該越耐越臭，起碼3日，<br />\n唔夠臭就繼續加乳酪，奶，豆漿，果d，<br />\n想要顏色就加下d涼茶丫，葛菜湯果d，又或者你鐘意可以試下酸辣粉果d湯底<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一定要打開個蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\nsize=4]<strong>一定要打開個蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>[/size=4]<br />\nsize=4]<strong>一定要打開個蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>[/size=4]<br />\n<br />\n<em><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">温馨提示：可以放係屋企/學校窗口平台外面比陽光曬[/b]</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本人學生時代整過，係可以由角落窗口位打開蓋，隔幾行都仲聞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d220a7509ea28f14d4345384fc781a29114caa","tid":1609493,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"經過今日 殺警都唔係問題 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609207</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"04d012fca50ec28909d3e695a0f3990abe1410f7","tid":1609493,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n義士既血不能白流 <br />\n絕對唔撚可以就咁算"},{"pid":"0071d099201148dc3ae9fd20ed2577937fa5078d","tid":1609493,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"有時間搞呢啲點解唔煉下火遁"},{"pid":"ad94baef19adfe0284ed5103ceaa22b4313785f5","tid":1609493,"uid":253320,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"Tear gas都吸過會驚臭臭魔法?"},{"pid":"75a2cea0b6da03d5e7d129cd9eb82af3b2e3c313","tid":1609493,"uid":263199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"萬物皆魔法，不過驚嘅人可以多d選項。<br />\n你怕比人査你學火魔法，<br />\n又怕有麵粉比人告就唔學水魔法，<br />\n蟲魔法你怕我都理解！<br />\n<br />\n咁臭臭魔法相對温和好多！！<br />\n有野飲好正常咋掛？"},{"pid":"a5bb41dcf91ecfd557bfb24515e06a2b52952ca8","tid":1609493,"uid":279689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:51:02.000Z","msg":"會唔會七傷拳，未打自己先死<br />\n而且個個有豬咀仲有冇用"},{"pid":"9c7d34b4b6376488400c518eb0c3627f4acb9160","tid":1609493,"uid":263199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0071d099201148dc3ae9fd20ed2577937fa5078d","tid":1609493,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:49:31.000Z","msg":"有時間搞呢啲點解唔煉下火遁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"因為好多人怕比人搜到物資，又或者物料唔方便比屋企人見到"},{"pid":"bd4aa772ee79bf997e79a2635ebe463d2a783f32","tid":1609493,"uid":263199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T14:57:27.000Z","msg":"其實好多popo都冇豬嘴，尤其橋上面果堆。<br />\n正如有巴打話齋，班popo on9架，自己食返自己d TG<br />\n都係因為佢地成日都冇<br />\n<br />\n另外！！！！佢地好鐘意埋伏係黨鐵站，然後落閘，成班企係裡面standby，仲可以同示威者對鬧<br />\n<br />\n你隔住個閘，又或者好似今日灣仔站旁邊位果到掉入去就得<br />\n<br />\n佢地局住企係到食"},{"pid":"600a0ca5c565853f75be262f8aa1e28b5c10d929","tid":1609493,"uid":327873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"覺得會臭翻自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89712c8f46a0f06b2af96c07e63a7118176e580d","tid":1609493,"uid":263199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"600a0ca5c565853f75be262f8aa1e28b5c10d929","tid":1609493,"uid":327873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:30:37.000Z","msg":"覺得會臭翻自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:41:07.000Z","msg":"豬隊友囉，正常你掉岀去應該唔會只掉前幾米掛？或者掉狗屋黨鐵"},{"pid":"1cb7078674ab8309054927c44e71802e0d35fe65","tid":1609493,"uid":10855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:42:14.000Z","msg":"點解唔玩色水彈"},{"pid":"6364535e2d646477ecb2e01e65afb7d9a06953c4","tid":1609493,"uid":169781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T10:47:53.000Z","msg":"奶臭得快"},{"pid":"2bad050322bf8f67933a4ec1ad98d7fc401fd666","tid":1609493,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:56:19.000Z","msg":"擺係地鐵站<br />\n人多既垃圾桶附近<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13248d372b7c3f63e62498e38f1099ed98282f9","tid":1609493,"uid":131696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:01:24.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好擺係消防喉轆個箱入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ea3c4cf8fdfa3be6e7fc86a55fb890d98ce3ba","tid":1609493,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:03:53.000Z","msg":"玩呢d , 咁同義和團有咩分別"},{"pid":"4e579ef35880564a0d0e551a6099791a76b6b01d","ti